text: Felipe Saturnino Gomes (born 10 August 1995), known as Felipe Saturnino, is a Brazilian footballer who most recently played for Madureira as a left back.Série D: Ex-lateral de Goiás e Juventus é apresentado como reforço do Novorizontino‚ futebolinterior.com.br, 29 May 2018 ==Club career== Born in Rio de Janeiro, Felipe Saturnino finished his formation with Goiás. On 18 October 2014 he made his first team – and Série A – debut, starting in a 0–0 home draw against Grêmio.Sem os artilheiros, Goiás e Grêmio amargam segundo empate sem gols (Without topscorers, Goiás and Grêmio bitter a second goalless draw); Globo Esporte, 18 October 2014 In November Felipe Saturnino renewed his link with the club, until 2017.De contrato novo, Saturnino quer iniciar o próximo ano voando no Goiás (With a new contract, Saturnino wants to start the following year flying at Goiás); Portal 730, 28 November 2014 ==References== ==External links== *Ogol profile * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Rio de Janeiro (city) Category:Brazilian footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Campeonato Brasileiro Série A players Category:Goiás Esporte Clube players
